        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Civil Rights Legacy Protection Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes it a crime to deface, damage, or destroy certain memorials that commemorate civil rights events or figures.</p> <p>An individual convicted under this act must pay restitution and is subject to additional penalties that vary based on the cost of the defacement, damage, or destruction.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
